Dx = (m_y-p_y+m_x*(k_x-p_x)/(p_y-k_y)-p_x*(p_y-k_y)/(p_x-k_x)) / ((k_x-p_x)/(p_y-k_y)-(p_y-k_y)/(p_x-k_x))
 Dy = (Dx-p_x)*(p_y-k_y)/(p_x-k_x)+p_y
s=(P_y-K_y)/(P_x-K_x)
