M_y-P_y
D_x = \frac{M_y-P_y - M_x/s-sP_x}{-s-1/s} \tag{1}
D_y-P_y = s(D_x-P_x) \\ D_y-M_y=-\frac{1}{s}(D_x-M_x)
M_y-P_y= -sP_x-\frac{1}{s}M_x +(s+1/s)D_x
D_x = \frac{M_y-P_y+sP_x+M_x/s}{s+1/s}\tag{2}
